	</div>
</div>

<div id="cannabisWrapper" class="row contentWrapper">
	<div class="content">
		<div class="row contentTitleWrapper">
			<h2 class="contentTitle">Medical Cannabis Cards</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="row contentTextWrapper">
			<p class="contentText">At Mountain Mental Health we strive to make the process of applying for a Utah State Medical Marijuana card as affordable, informative, and easy as possible. Call for an in-person appointment with a qualified medical provider (QMP) at <a href="tel:385-449-9990">(385) 449-9990</a> Our QMP's will meet with you and evaluate if you have a qualifying condition which makes you eligible for a medical marijuana card during a short 15–20-minute visit.</p>
			<h3 id="cannabisPricingTitle">Pricing</h3>
			<p class="cannabisText">Initial one-year medical marijuana card: $180</p>
			<p class="cannabisText">One year renewal: $80</p>
			<p><i>Note: you must be 21 years of age to apply for a medical marijuana card</i></p>
			<p>Utah medical cannabis pharmacy locations can be found <a href="https://medicalcannabis.utah.gov/pharmacies/pharmacy-locations/">here</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="content contentImageWrapper">
		<img src="assets/img/services/cannabis.png" alt="cannabis-logo" class="contentImage" />
	</div>
</div>

